{
  "texts": [
    "Each participating institution in the cohort formed a research team, received interview training from Ithaka S+R, and conducted semi-structured interviews at their respective institutions using Ithaka S+R's interview guide.",
    "Ithaka S+R also conducted supplemental interviews to enhance disciplinary diversity.",
    "The interviews were conducted between March and May 2024.",
    "Each institution's team and Ithaka S+R conducted an average of 12 to 13 interviews, for a combined total of 246 interviews.",
    "Institutional teams were not given restrictions in their selection of interviewees in terms of department or rank; the interviews represent a wide range of disciplines and career stages."
  ]
}